	(text "Power tree per badge_hw_design.md §Power tree.\nUSB-C VBUS → TP4056 → BAT (cell+ via J11) → slide switch → ME6211C33 → +3V3 rail.\nTP4056 PROG = 2.4k → 500 mA charge. VBAT div 100k/100k → VBAT_SENSE → MCU GP26/ADC0.\nTP4056 CHRG̅ → 100k pullup to 3V3 → ~CHRG → MCU GP18.\nCC1 / CC2 each → 5.1k → GND (UFP advertise).\nUSB_DP / USB_DM route through 27R series on MCU_Core to RP2040." (exclude_from_sim no) (at 28.00 35.00 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left top)) (uuid "d4be2d81-6e97-49ae-90e8-c1cf261ed0df"))
